<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Clean Email Template</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: #F5F5F5;
      color: #000000;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    
    .email-header {
      padding: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e057ff, #CC0DF8);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    
    .header-title {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    
    .email-content {
      padding: 40px 32px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: #000000;
    }
    
    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: #000000;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .highlight-box {
      background-color: #FCF1FF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    
    .highlight-title {
      color: #78158E;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    
    .highlight-content {
      margin: 0;
      color: #000000;
    }
    
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 32px 0;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .coins-section {
      margin: 32px 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #coins-card-top, #coins-card-bottom);
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .coins-icon {
      color: #F4900C;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .coins-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #000000;
    }
    
    .notification-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #04D900;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    
    .email-footer {
      padding: 24px 32px;
      background-color: #FCF1FF;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .footer-links {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .footer-link {
      color: #78158E;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 12px;
    }
    
    .copyright {
      color: #78158E;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #FAE2FF;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-content {
        padding: 32px 24px;
      }
      
      .header-title {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/120x40" alt="Logo" class="logo">
      <h1 class="header-title">Welcome to Our Platform {{name}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-content">
      <p class="greeting">Hello Jane,</p>
      
      <p class="message">
        Thank you for joining our platform. We're excited to have you on board and can't wait to help you get started on your journey with us.
      </p>
      
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="highlight-title">Your account is ready</h2>
        <p class="highlight-content">
          You can now access all features of our platform. Start exploring and make the most of your experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="message">
        To help you get started, we've prepared some resources that will guide you through the main features of our platform.
      </p>
      
      <a href="#" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
      
      <div class="divider"></div>
      
      <p class="message">
        <span class="notification-badge"></span>
        <strong>New feature available:</strong> You can now customize your profile with our new themes and options.
      </p>
      
      <div class="coins-section">
        <div class="coins-icon">ðŸª™</div>
        <h3 class="coins-title">You have 100 bonus coins</h3>
        <p class="highlight-content">Use them to unlock premium content and features</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-footer">
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Terms of Service</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Unsubscribe</a>
      </div>
      <p class="copyright">Â© 2023 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
